  "instructions": [
    "Heat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat",
    "Thread the Frankfurter sausage onto skewers",
    "Grill the Frankfurter for 3-4 minutes on each side, or until cooked through",
    "Meanwhile, heat the coconut milk and palm sugar in a saucepan over medium heat",
    "Bring the coconut milk mixture to a simmer and cook for 2-3 minutes, or until thickened",
    "Remove the Frankfurter from the grill and add to the coconut milk sauce",
    "Toss to coat the Frankfurter in the sauce",
    "Garnish with cilantro and serve in copper mugs",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional cilantro if desired"
